By: Thomas Traherne
Tags:
  - Creation=Man’s Primordial Birthright
Note: |
  Gloss on Psalm VII
Reference:
  - Title: Psalms
    Chapter: VII
---
This glory and honor wherewith man is crowned ought to affect every person
that is grateful, with celestial joy： and so much the rather because it
is every man’s proper and sole inheritance.
